Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要降落到地面上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉到左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行 前進的道路被妨礙了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉飛進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 要崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}藍\N  \N色\N  \N的\N  \N雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行 這是媽媽的份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的~巴隆 你最近太肥了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 早飯已經做好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 幾點了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經8點多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去上學了 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是浮游靈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道自己死了 還在大街上彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 那樣的靈 絕對不能和它說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和它說話了 就會被它拖進靈界去了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像討論的很熱烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保的超常現象解說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說2班的涼子 在教會暗巷裏看到幽靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 還是穿著黑色外套的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 鈴聲已經響了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回座位 回座位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假活動在班會結束以後再討論吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪惠老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 藤原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假 和我約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾 約會的日程都已經排滿到三年後了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下課時間 回家路上請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊上不要跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 明天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要不要一起去試膽量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那太好了 我們去找幽靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試膽量?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是暑假 大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:04:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧 試膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試膽量?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對啦 是去找幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 還是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還相信幽靈什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西怎麼可能有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學性的根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上還有很多科學無法解釋的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢 幽靈什麼的沒有 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那我們就去證實一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就決定了 藤原也要一起去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 為什麼我一定要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是害怕幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才...才不是害怕呢 幽靈什麼的 對吧 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有私塾要去 所以不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做感覺很不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 佑那傢伙最近都不怎麼合群了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒辦法啊 後藤要參加中學考試的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在這裏待到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田 你知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始就是暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這五年 連休假日都沒有...啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在德國不也發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝做一副很懂的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給本部的報告你準備怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是這樣的資料 本部也不會重視的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要更加努力了呢 內田~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被郡山指手劃腳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 抽煙請你到車外去抽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 都到這個時間了 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始是寫作講習了 你知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假只能集中精神在學習上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話 一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 還是不要再和學校的同學們交往了比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試膽量?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天晚上 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是暑假 但也不能總是玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在工作嗎 這午飯還是我做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:07:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面有些奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是抱怨的話 媽媽你自己做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在原稿完成之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是約定好的做飯都交給你了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不要抱怨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個女人獨自養育孩子是非常辛苦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是還從爸爸那裏拿了撫養費的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事情我還是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明年就是中學生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說媽媽工作是不可以的嗎 啊 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可總畫一些賣不出去的連環畫也沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託不要說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習到這個時間 好努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在私塾前面等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚還出來 會被綁架的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那麼擔心我 就不要離家出走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你說要離家出走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你說想去東京的父親那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 我們離家出走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去東京吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候是和媽媽吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家父母又離婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況很複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡說了 信以為真的我才是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 等一下 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離家出走如果不好好考慮一下的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算離家出走了 也只不過是很快就被找到帶回家罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情我都明白 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不可能離開這個城市的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等成為大人了 什麼地方都可以去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我不是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭當小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 想快點變成大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我變的不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑...啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沙夜子那裏收到了郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說前天晚上 在商店街出現了無頭幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 還披著黑色斗篷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色斗篷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色斗篷的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃~~等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂啦 那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會呢 快告訴我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 小姐們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的家是在這附近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔有些想調查的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們喝果汁呀 不過是罐裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 差點忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人 一定是變態啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你也這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快聯絡警察吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 雖然有些可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 郡山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 內山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京的觀測衛星的資料分析好像已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯 已經確認了異常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼最近要待在這裏一段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備怎麼辦 今後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在考慮呢 在山上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去私塾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試膽量這種事好無聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是啊 這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 才...才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 來了 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙怎麼看起來很高興的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 鬼門已經打開的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳下也不安全 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀呀 藤原原來是個膽小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快點走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向井這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定其實她不相信幽靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼那 快來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像看到光了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 一定是鬼火 鬼火飛出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 啊 鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也來得及 馬上去私塾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信 你竟然做了這樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等一下 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然和這樣的小孩交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座標已固定 倒數計時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是掃興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要認真的祈禱 為了見到幽靈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好 大家一起祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈 幽靈 請快現身 快快現身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是搞錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在擔心後藤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙有什麼事都寫在臉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私塾打電話聯絡說 你沒有去上課
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的晚上 就幾個小孩子一起出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙也在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的母親對小孩太放縱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...正漸漸變的不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停車...停車！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪 藍色的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 仲夏怎麼會下雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向井 已經夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 直到看見幽靈之前決不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:19:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子也餓了 差不多也該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 看不見了 看不見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是電池沒電了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向井
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子 那一定是樹的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 美保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不可能 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不....可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 美保
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要奪回的是上乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其餘的不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高密度的離子反應
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈不是應該沒有腿的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是真正的幽靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛 那不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪也是正常的啊  因為是幽靈嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 大家快走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼飛過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃 快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是靈啊 是恐怖的靈啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 是沖著我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在 沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪兒去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
